                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000341d6368-5b62-4155-86cf-d5408c8a98f4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(cos\ {θ}=\frac{1-{tan}^{2}\ {\frac{θ}{2}}}{1+{tan}^{2}\ {\frac{θ}{2}}}\ \ ⇒\frac{4}{5}=\frac{1-{tan}^{2}\ {\frac{θ}{2}}}{1+{tan}^{2}\ {\frac{θ}{2}}}\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001341d6368-5b62-4155-86cf-d5408c8a98f4"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000341d6368-5b62-4155-86cf-d5408c8a98f4 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001341d6368-5b62-4155-86cf-d5408c8a98f4 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000094b9d26d-94b8-43bd-a185-9dbd4b713425" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒9{tan}^{2}\ {\frac{θ}{2}}=1\ ⇒{tan}^{2}\ {\frac{θ}{2}}=\frac{1}{9}∴tan\ {\frac{θ}{2}}=±\frac{1}{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000194b9d26d-94b8-43bd-a185-9dbd4b713425">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000094b9d26d-94b8-43bd-a185-9dbd4b713425 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000194b9d26d-94b8-43bd-a185-9dbd4b713425 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
