                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-000000ec0a79cc-49ba-45d2-83e6-8c12a06365eb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{1-cos\ {x}}{{x}^{2}}}=?⁡\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ec0a79cc-49ba-45d2-83e6-8c12a06365eb"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ec0a79cc-49ba-45d2-83e6-8c12a06365eb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ec0a79cc-49ba-45d2-83e6-8c12a06365eb {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
