                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000a75f28e6-a0e6-4a8c-a5ce-4daa410fdb82" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{1-cos\ {x}}{{x}^{2}}}=\ \underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{2{sin}^{2}\ {\frac{x}{2}}}{{x}^{2}}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a75f28e6-a0e6-4a8c-a5ce-4daa410fdb82"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {{\left(\frac{sin\ {\frac{x}{2}}}{\frac{x}{2}}\right)}^{2}}\times \frac{1}{4}\times 2=\frac{1}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a75f28e6-a0e6-4a8c-a5ce-4daa410fdb82"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a75f28e6-a0e6-4a8c-a5ce-4daa410fdb82 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a75f28e6-a0e6-4a8c-a5ce-4daa410fdb82 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000073d7699-1c9a-4b38-baa6-ee4c9c11ab10" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001073d7699-1c9a-4b38-baa6-ee4c9c11ab10">Alternative: </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{1-cos\ {x}}{{x}^{2}}}\left[ \frac{0}{0}\right] =\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{sin\ {x}}{2x}}\left[ \frac{0}{0}\right] \) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000073d7699-1c9a-4b38-baa6-ee4c9c11ab10 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001073d7699-1c9a-4b38-baa6-ee4c9c11ab10 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c295c6c0-92a5-4fc0-8fd8-cb21b5ea9d1d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\underset{x→0}{lim}\ {\frac{cos\ {x}}{2}}=\frac{1}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c295c6c0-92a5-4fc0-8fd8-cb21b5ea9d1d"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c295c6c0-92a5-4fc0-8fd8-cb21b5ea9d1d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c295c6c0-92a5-4fc0-8fd8-cb21b5ea9d1d {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
