                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000066ecf304-02a9-4014-ad10-66e8d107c9b5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><a id="_Hlk166765879" class="pt-00000166ecf304-02a9-4014-ad10-66e8d107c9b5"></a><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(f(x)=x(12-2x{)}^{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000266ecf304-02a9-4014-ad10-66e8d107c9b5">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({f}^{{'}}\left(x\right)=144-96x+12{x}^{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000266ecf304-02a9-4014-ad10-66e8d107c9b5">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000066ecf304-02a9-4014-ad10-66e8d107c9b5 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}a.pt-00000166ecf304-02a9-4014-ad10-66e8d107c9b5 {text-decoration: none;}span.pt-00000266ecf304-02a9-4014-ad10-66e8d107c9b5 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cfe7ea01-a92c-4537-87f3-51085d29e6ae" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴12{x}^{2}-96x+144=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cfe7ea01-a92c-4537-87f3-51085d29e6ae"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cfe7ea01-a92c-4537-87f3-51085d29e6ae {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001cfe7ea01-a92c-4537-87f3-51085d29e6ae {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f53d6642-729b-4655-a22f-cb40f42dd468" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f53d6642-729b-4655-a22f-cb40f42dd468">ev, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({x}^{2}-8x+12=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001f53d6642-729b-4655-a22f-cb40f42dd468"> ev, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=6,2\) </span><span class="pt-000001f53d6642-729b-4655-a22f-cb40f42dd468">;</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f53d6642-729b-4655-a22f-cb40f42dd468 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f53d6642-729b-4655-a22f-cb40f42dd468 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003aed0898-9729-4751-aae2-8f6cd97d529d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({F}^{″}\left(x\right)=-96+24x\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013aed0898-9729-4751-aae2-8f6cd97d529d">; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=2\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013aed0898-9729-4751-aae2-8f6cd97d529d"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000023aed0898-9729-4751-aae2-8f6cd97d529d">Gi Rb&#168; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({f}^{″}&lt;0\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003aed0898-9729-4751-aae2-8f6cd97d529d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013aed0898-9729-4751-aae2-8f6cd97d529d {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000023aed0898-9729-4751-aae2-8f6cd97d529d {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001faf8d2d-8a23-4117-8ca4-b5f73d46b415" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\ f(2)=128\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011faf8d2d-8a23-4117-8ca4-b5f73d46b415">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-