                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000057cfeb15-9465-493b-89d5-1fabe25570dc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(arg\left(-1+i\right)=π-{tan}^{-1}\ {\left| \frac{1}{-1}\right| }=\frac{3π}{4}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000157cfeb15-9465-493b-89d5-1fabe25570dc"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000057cfeb15-9465-493b-89d5-1fabe25570dc {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000157cfeb15-9465-493b-89d5-1fabe25570dc {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
